00:01:24.199 --> 00:01:27.240
it’s a state of mind, a shorthand for a

00:01:27.250 --> 00:01:29.619
whole set of values and attitudes, which

00:01:29.750 --> 00:01:31.979
are either espoused vigorously by the

00:01:31.979 --> 00:01:34.849
